00:22:12.399 --> 00:22:17.399
vegn der shlang, vegn Berte Grosman,

00:22:17.399 --> 00:22:21.439
vil ikh dertseyln eyn zakh vos iz shoyn a zeyer a shpeterdike.

00:22:21.439 --> 00:22:26.239
vos iz farbundn mitn geto, ober ikh meyn az ikh ken es itster dertseyln.

00:22:26.499 --> 00:22:34.200
in geto hobn zikh in zeyer a shlekhte lage gefinen di inteligents.

00:22:34.279 --> 00:22:36.959
mentshn vos flegn aroysgeyn arbetn

00:22:36.959 --> 00:22:41.079
flegn khotsh dort bay der arbet opesn dem teler zup,

00:22:41.079 --> 00:22:45.680
